    "Puromycin (2.5 mg ml -1) selection was started 2 days after transduction.",
    "Selection continued for 7 days, after which puromycin was removed for the remainder of the screen.",
    "Cells were maintained in exponential growth by isolating and removing a fraction of cells every 2-3 days.",
    "We analyzed data from two time points at approximately 14 and 21 days.",
    "DNA was extracted from cells with a Blood and Cell Culture DNA Mini kit (Qiagen)."
